flowchart TD
    A[Captured Scan Data] --> B{Detection Rule Matching}
    B --> C1[Advertising Rules]
    B --> C2[Tracking Pixel Rules]
    B --> C3[Analytics Rules]

    C1 --> D[Matched Evidence Collected]
    C2 --> D
    C3 --> D

    D --> E[Evidence Weighted by Type]
    E --> F[Diminishing-Returns Aggregation]
    F --> G[Raw Score Normalized 0-100]
    G --> H{Score Range}
    H -->|75-100| I[High Confidence]
    H -->|40-74| J[Medium Confidence]
    H -->|1-39| K[Low Confidence]
    H -->|0| L[No Detection - Excluded from Results]

    I --> M[Persisted to Database]
    J --> M
    K --> M
